<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang='en'>
<head>
	<meta charset='UTF-8'>
	<title>Password Reset</title>
	<style>
		body {
			margin: 0;
			padding: 0;
			background-color: #f5f5f5;
			font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
		}

		.email-container {
			max-width: 600px;
			margin: 30px auto;
			background-color: #ffffff;
			border: 1px solid #dddddd;
			border-radius: 8px;
			padding: 30px;
		}

		.header {
			text-align: center;
			margin-bottom: 25px;
		}

		.header h1 {
			font-family: 'Courgette', cursive;
			color: #026dd1;
			font-size: 32px;
			margin: 0;
		}

		.header p {
			color: #666666;
			font-size: 14px;
			margin-top: 8px;
		}

		.content {
			font-size: 16px;
			color: #333333;
			line-height: 1.6;
		}

		.button-wrapper {
			margin: 30px 0;
			text-align: center;
		}

		.button {
			background-color: #026DD1;
			color: #ffffff !important;
			padding: 12px 24px;
			border: none;
			border-radius: 6px;
			text-decoration: none;
			font-weight: bold;
			display: inline-block;
		}

		.footer {
			margin-top: 40px;
			font-size: 14px;
			color: #999999;
			text-align: center;
		}

		.button:visited,
		.button:hover,
		.button:active {
			color: #ffffff !important;
			text-decoration: none;
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class='email-container'>
	<div class='header'>
		<h1>Aspire</h1>
		<p>The Aspiration Abyss</p>
	</div>
	<div class='content'>
		<p>Hello <strong>{{ current_user }}</strong>,</p>
		<p>Weâ€™ve received a request to reset your password.</p>
		<p>Please click the button below to proceed:</p>
		<div class='button-wrapper'>
			<a
					class='button'
					href='{{ reset_password_url }}'>Reset Password</a>
		</div>
		<p>If you did not request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
	</div>
	<div class='footer'>
		Best regards,<br>
		The Aspire Team
	</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
